item.description: Another great meet up, a night of Blues with Satch, Cindy, Clint, Terri Lee and friends at Mal's Lounge @ George's Restaurant in Haverhill Ma. This is the last chance to see Satch and Cindy perform before leaving for Memphis to compete for an international Blues Challenge Title. Please ask for Satch, Clint or Terri Lee at this meet up with Boston Millionaires.
item.how_to_find_us: Pleaes ask for Satch, Cindy, Clint or Terri Lee.
